== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Komatsu Seiren|ja|小松清廉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Rikugyaku Nan|ja|陸羯南|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a political critic and journalist († {{ill|1907|ja|1907|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ikamasa Hisaya|ja|岩崎久弥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an entrepreneur and 3rd head of the Mitsubishi zaibatsu († {{ill|1955|ja|1955|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Takegoshi Yosaburō|ja|竹越與三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a member of the House of Representatives and member of the House of Peers, historian and critic († {{ill|1950|ja|1950|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
