{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 14''' is the 14th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|ja|Tenpyō-hōji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|764|ja|764|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Junnin|ja|淳仁天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (the deposed emperor) was exiled to Awaji. * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1720|ja|1720|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Paper merchant Jiyobei and Kii merchant Koharu committed double suicide; later dramatized by {{ill|Chikamatsu Monzaemon|ja|近松門左衛門|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in "Shin-chū Tenmōjima". * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Taisei Hōkan (return of political power) took place as {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} submitted a memorandum to the court.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Komatsu Seiren|ja|小松清廉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Rikugyaku Nan|ja|陸羯南|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a political critic and journalist († {{ill|1907|ja|1907|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ikamasa Hisaya|ja|岩崎久弥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an entrepreneur and 3rd head of the Mitsubishi zaibatsu († {{ill|1955|ja|1955|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Takegoshi Yosaburō|ja|竹越與三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a member of the House of Representatives and member of the House of Peers, historian and critic († {{ill|1950|ja|1950|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshōjingo|ja|Tenpyō神護|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|765|ja|765|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Junnin|ja|淳仁天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 47th emperor. * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1669|ja|1669|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the Ainu chief. * {{ill|Taihei Kōkoku|ja|太平興国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|976|ja|976|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Taizu), the first emperor of the Northern Song (* {{ill|927|ja|927|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an agrarian reformer (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
