== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835}} {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日}} ） – {{ill|Komatsu Seiren|ja|小松清廉}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1870|ja|1870}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日}} ） – {{ill|Rikugyaku Nan|ja|陸羯南}} , a political critic and journalist († {{ill|1907|ja|1907}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日}} ） – {{ill|Ikamasa Hisaya|ja|岩崎久弥}} , an entrepreneur and 3rd head of the Mitsubishi zaibatsu († {{ill|1955|ja|1955}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日}} ） – {{ill|Takegoshi Yosaburō|ja|竹越與三郎}} , a member of the House of Representatives and member of the House of Peers, historian and critic († {{ill|1950|ja|1950}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshōjingo|ja|Tenpyō神護}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|765|ja|765}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Junnin|ja|淳仁天皇}} , the 47th emperor. * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1669|ja|1669}} {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日}} ） – {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン}} , the Ainu chief. * {{ill|Taihei Kōkoku|ja|太平興国}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|976|ja|976}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤}} (Taizu), the first emperor of the Northern Song (* {{ill|927|ja|927}} ). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127}} {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家}} (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045}} ). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日}} ） – {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳}} , an agrarian reformer (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787}} ).
