=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Paper merchant Jiyobei and Kii merchant Koharu committed double suicide; later dramatized by {{ill|Chikamatsu Monzaemon|ja|近松門左衛門|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in "Shin-chū Tenmōjima". * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The Taisei Hōkan (return of political power) took place as {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} submitted a memorandum to the court.
