er:Immanuelle/November 11|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Junnin|ja|淳仁天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junnin|qq=}} (the deposed emperor) was exiled to Awaji. * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1720|ja|1720|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1720|qq=}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 13|qq=}} ） – Paper merchant Jiyobei and Kii merchant Koharu committed double suicide; later dramatized by {{ill|Chikamatsu Monzaemon|ja|近松門左衛門|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chikamatsu Monzaemon|qq=}} in "Shin-chū Tenmōjima". * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} ） – The Taisei Hōkan (return of political power) took place as {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yoshinobu|qq=}} submitted a memorandum to the court.
